 from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}